        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figures 2 - 7. Pusulissus phiaoacensis sp. nov. 2 adult (holotype), dorsal view 3 adult (holotype), lateral view 4 head and thorax (holotype), dorsal view 5 adult (holotype), frontal view 6 forewing (paratype) 7 hindwing (paratype). Scale bars: 1 mm." , "Figures 8 - 12. Pusulissus phiaoacensis sp. nov., male, holotype. 8 genitalia, lateral view 9 anal tube, dorsal view 10 gonostylus, lateral view 11 phallic complex, right lateral view 12 phallic complex, ventral view. Scale bars: 0.2 mm." , "Figures 13 - 14. Pusulissus phiaoacensis sp. nov., male, holotype. 13 phallic complex, right lateral view 14 apex of phallic complex, posterior view. Abbreviations: dll: dorso-lateral lobe of periandrium; Ade: Aedeagus; vl: ventral lobe of periandrium; Adep: Aedeagus processes. Scale bars: 0.2 mm." , "Figures 21 - 24. Habitus and habitat of Pusulissus phiaoacensis sp. nov. 21 - 23 habitus in nature (Photo G. Kunz) 24 habitat (Photo T. Bourgoin)." , "Figure 46. Bayesian 50 % consensus tree of Parahiraciini species based on combined sequences (18 S, 28 S, COXI, Cytb) with 2 species of Sarimini and 2 species of Hemisphaeriini as outgroup. At each node, values denote posterior probability support." , "Figures 15 - 20. Pusulissus phiaoacensis sp. nov., female, paratype. 15 anal tube, dorsal view 16 gonoplac, lateral view 17 gonapophysis IX and gonospiculum bridge, dorsal view 18 gonapophysis IX and gonospiculum bridge, lateral view 19 sternite VII, ventral view 20 gonocoxa VIII and gonapophysis VIII, lateral view. Scale bars: 0.2 mm." ;
